OL,5, Concerns about a road built through a  
OL,6, graveyard are being investigated by    
OL,7, police.                                
OL,9,FFamilies of people buried at Bethany   
OL,10,FChapel, in Hodley, Powys, claim        
OL,11,Fheadstones had been moved and some have
OL,12,Feven gone missing.                     
OL,14,FDolafon Gospel Hall Trust, part of     
OL,15,FPlymouth Brethren Christian Church, is 
OL,16,Frenovating the chapel for use as a     
OL,17,Fmeeting place.                         
OL,19,FIt denied works had resulted in        
OL,20,Fgravestones being lost.                
